data.name: label1.Text
data.value: For journey of longer distances though we have airways most of the people use the railways, which is most convenient, affordable means of transport. So keeping this in view, the reservation of railways is a most important task and it must be faster and efficient as the demand (travellers) is very high. In order to meet this demand, manual reservation is completely ruled out and it requires an efficient program to implement the online reservation.
